npcs.dialogue:
{cyan}You have come seeking passage. I sense {bold}courage{/} in you.
Take this key — it opens the chest in the treasury.
But beware the {red}idol{/}. Its touch means death.{/}

rooms.description:
Gold coins are scattered across the floor, but most of the {yellow}treasure{/}
has long been looted. An {yellow}ornate chest{/} sits on a raised platform,
still sealed. In the corner, a {red}dark idol{/} sits on a pedestal.
